Incident replay and forensics

Usage: franken-node incident <COMMAND>

Commands:
  bundle          Export deterministic incident bundle
  replay          Replay incident timeline locally
  counterfactual  Simulate alternative policy actions
  list            List recorded incidents
  help            Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
